Lunarpine stood near the cave opening looking back. shadow wing was 
to far away to see but he did smell her. quickly he circled around. 
she was within a couple miles of him, he smelled the sweet scent of 
her feathers, he thought he could hear the whistleing wind as she 
beat her wings. she'd continued north where he turned off."To the pit 
with the caves,"He looked to the sky and in his deepest most vibrant 
voice did something he hadn't done since joining the Maximals.

HOOOOOOOOOOOOWWWWWWWWWWWLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLLL


His voice echoed, his mech fluid boiled, at last there was hunter and 
prey, he didn't know at the moment which he was, he just knew that 
once shadow wing heard his cry of the wild, she'd know that she'd 
just become the prey.

 > (Much better logo, I knew you had the fighting spirit.)
> "FEATHER WIEGHT BIRDBRAIN?! You four legged walking flea circus!"
> She flew after him.  She could tell by the signal that she was 
> getting closer to him. She noticed that he was headed north.  She 
> smiled. If he thought that he could lose her in the frozen north, 
he 
> was wrong on that count.
>
